snippet.title: Arcane Quest 3 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Arcane Quest 3 is a mobile and desktop RPG game available on Android, iOS and Windows 10. 

It's based on classic tabletop games such as Hero Quest, Dragonstrike and D&D. 

Join an epic fantasy story, restore the honor of your guild and defeat evil creatures in this incredible adventure.

Follow us at:
http://www.nexgamestudios.com
http://www.arcanequestgame.com

Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/arcanequest3
